frames.caption: A whimsical scene depicts miniature construction workers interacting with a large pan of bulgur and meatballs. The workers are using ladders and ropes, with a toy crane assisting in their playful construction-like activities. The setting creates an imaginative blend of culinary and construction themes.
frames.description: The scene is a creative setup where miniature figures are styled as construction workers, engaging with a large dish of food as if it were a construction site. The playful interaction between the tiny figures and the oversized food elements creates a humorous and imaginative atmosphere.
